text: Lang Lang (born 1982) is a Chinese pianist. Lang Lang may also refer to: * Lang Lang, Victoria, a town in Australia * Lang Lang River, a river in Gippsland, Victoria, Australia * A character from the Japanese manga Steam Detectives ==See also== *Cananga odorata, a tree valued for its perfume whose common names include Ylang-ylang and ilang-ilang
title: Lang Lang (disambiguation)
